        {
            "Key": "disclaimer_text",
            "Value": "By accepting 5 pennies/year you agree: \n- to become non-human; an 'alpha-test subject' with a dynamic collar, tectonic judo and light bulbs that violate your sanity; \n- not to protest when anomalies take your money, plumber Bob - the remnants of your dignity, and the laws of physics - your socks."
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_authors_title",
            "Value": "who are the authors"
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_authors_text",
            "Value": "Team Podzabornykh Trolley, which has four members. \n\nOleg Nikiforov - Sound Designer; \nYaroslava Belyaeva - 3D modeler + texture artist; \nIlya Varankin - PM and too many small tasks here and there to list; \nSergey Konovalov - coder and jack of all trades. (Those scary animations are mine)"
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_what_to_do_title",
            "Value": "what to do"
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_what_to_do_text",
            "Value": "Besides suffering and dying, work as a warehouse worker - open a crate with [Use], take the needed item to the right shelf. What the magical black board requires, take that item from the shelf to delivery."
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_why_empty_title",
            "Value": "why so empty"
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_why_empty_text",
            "Value": "One word - AMBITION. We planned too much for two weeks. Some of the jokes we made either work at a basic level or are like tinsel - pretty, gets in the way, but nothing more."
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_broken_title",
            "Value": "something broke"
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_broken_text",
            "Value": "Unfortunately not surprising, even predictable; it would be more surprising to see no one opening this window. I pray it doesn't break the game, just the incomprehensible atmosphere at most. If it does break the game - kick me - the coder. Somehow. Yell at me!"
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_updates_title",
            "Value": "will it be updated?"
        },
        {
            "Key": "help_updates_text",
            "Value": "No promises."
